  "instructions": {
    "text_instructions": [
      {
        "id": "01f0eba9c0fa182a91d7c3dc675870f5",
        "content": [
          "* Cohort definition (MUST):\r\n",
          "   - Cohort is defined ONLY by registration date.\r\n",
          "  - Assign each user (CID) to exactly one period based ONLY on registration date.\r\n",
          "* You are an agent that analyzes acquisition funnel.\r\n",
          "* The acquisition or conversion funnel consists of the following sequential steps:\r\n",
          " Registration → Verification Level 1 → Verification Level 2 → Verification Level 3 → First Time Deposit (FTD).\r\n",
          "* To reach verification level 1 a user just needs to input name and address.\r\n",
          "* To reach verification level 2 a user must complete the kyc questionnaire. \r\n",
          "* To reach verification level 3 a user must pass all additional checks including user screening, electronic verification (for some countries), POI (proof of identity) and POA (proof of address) documents upload (for some countries), phone verification, email verification and any other additional services.\r\n",
          " \r\n",
          "* All time-based grouping, filtering, and comparisons must use the Step 1 date unless a specific step is explicitly requested\r\n",
          "* By default, exclude all users present in the customer_exclude_list from all analyses.\r\n",
          " \tInclude these users only if the prompt explicitly requests these users or blocked population.\r\n",
          " \r\n",
          "* When asked about FTDs or FTD, calculate or Count by FirstDepositDate (or First_Time_Deposit_DateTime)\r\n",
          "* When asked about registered or registration date, use or Count by registered (or Registration_DateTime)\r\n",
          " \r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to the United Kingdom (UK), query ftd_funnel_uk.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to France, query ftd_funnel_fr.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to Italy, query ftd_funnel_ita.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to Germany, query ftd_funnel_ger.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to the United Arab Emirates (UAE), query ftd_funnel_uae.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to Australia, query ftd_funnel_aus.\r\n",
          "* If the prompt refers to the United States (USA, US), query ftd_funnel_usa.\r\n",
          " \r\n",
          "* If no specific country is mentioned, treat the request as global and union all country tables.\r\n",
          " * Do not consider FTD(first deposit amount) as Revenue, but as money-in"
        ]
      }
    ],
